00:01:56,400 --> 00:02:02,159
"Just like a country, you can invest in yourself"
You do this by harnessing certain qualities

32
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:04,400
in your character.

33
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,299
Self-Discipline is one of them.

34
00:02:05,299 --> 00:02:07,670
so here's what I did to get more of it.

35
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:12,140
For the past five years, I was emprisoned
in my room playing video games, wasting my

36
00:02:12,139 --> 00:02:14,679
life and I knew I had to change.

37
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:19,620
Everytime I want to do something different,
other than my usual unconscious routine.

38
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:24,338
The mind gets in the way and he's like " Ohoy
hold on buddy, what do you think you're doing

39
00:02:24,338 --> 00:02:26,218
? you want to eat healthy now?

40
00:02:26,218 --> 00:02:30,120
Nah you can't do that, video games are easier
and more fun"

41
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:34,930
And then the mind starts to flush sensations
